reviews.text: Clean, affordable, busy, and large selection of food. Raw meats, drinks, side dishes, beef, and the like all underneath one flat rate price.  Don't eat too much of one thing or attempt to get your money's worth as I did.  Great food and at a wonderful price.
The meat was marinated just right. The service is quite nice. Dessert needs a bit of improvement.
Great place to eat. Pick the meat and vegetables and cook in the grill on the centre table.
Tasty ribs and many variety food. Also have dessert, soup and salmon sashimi. The reason why I don't give 5 start is there is no parking privilege. Parking rate in this building is HKD $32 per hour.
Huge range of food, both Korean and Cantonese, all you can eat with most drinks included as well. Great value for money

reviews.text: Clean, affordable, busy, and large selection of food. Raw meats, drinks, side dishes, beef, and the like all underneath one flat rate price.  Don't eat too much of one thing or attempt to get your money's worth as I did.  Great food and at a wonderful price.
好過二期那間韓燒,但仍一般,漢x苑味比這好
食物種類很多，熟食也有水準，服務態度良好，價錢合理！唯一不足的是沒有刺身。
價錢非常合理，任飲任食2人吃午餐都只是$293，當爐架燒燶時，可以即時通知職員更換，地方非常大，冷氣也非常足夠🤗

reviews.text: Very convenient. Just next to MTR.
Ok
Nice
Many restaurants
今天在家開車過來的，🥴可是這裡好像沒有停車場。在假日期間，附近的停車場也沒有提供時租的車位，所以今天只能停泊在路邊一下。這裡有很多餐廳，有一些賣電腦用品的店。今天去了在二樓的漢和韓國料理餐廳，主要是自助餐形式的烤肉餐廳。覺得口味不錯，像以前在香港的舊式韓國烤肉餐廳。覺得反而比吃牛肉主題的烤肉店來說，吃的種類比較多和較便宜一些。
